It’s already a new year?! Let’s share our surprise… this time in 47 languages! All of these translations are based on suggestions from readers. THANK YOU to everyone who helped me! You’ll find all the cartoons in full size on my Hedger Humor Facebook page and on my website at www.HedgerHumor.com. You’ll also find a blank cartoon that you can fill in, in case you don’t see your language here! 

It was so fun to create these different versions, but it also took a lot of time — so in February we will be back to one cartoon in English. I might do another translation later this year, and if that’s the case, I’ll announce it ahead of time! 

P.S. I’m nervous that I messed something up, and if that’s the case I’m so sorry! I tried really hard to get everything correct. For more on how all the translations came about — and answers to questions you may have — see the post on my website. 

Happy New Year, everyone! 

#hedgerhumor #newmonth #timeflies
